    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not-assessed at level 1, which is permissible under ASME V&V 40 Table 1 for a Class II device at MRL 2. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the hemolysis prediction claim. Decision recorded without reference to a defined Context of Use document.",
